<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Your Subscription - <%= app_name %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #007bff;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .welcome-title {
            color: #28a745;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .plan-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .plan-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .plan-price {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .features {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .features h3 {
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .features ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .features li {
            padding: 5px 0;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }
        .features li:before {
            content: "âœ“";
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }
        .next-billing {
            background: #e7f3ff;
            border: 1px solid #007bff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .next-billing h3 {
            color: #007bff;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }
        .support {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo"><%= app_name %></div>
            <div class="welcome-title">ðŸŽ‰ Welcome to Your Subscription!</div>
        </div>

        <p>Hello <strong><%= garage_name %></strong>,</p>

        <p>Congratulations! Your subscription has been successfully activated. You now have access to all the premium features of your chosen plan.</p>

        <div class="plan-details">
            <div class="plan-name"><%= plan_name %></div>
            <div class="plan-price"><%= price_formatted %> <%= currency %></div>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
            <h3>ðŸš€ What's Included:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Premium garage management tools</li>
                <li>Advanced booking management</li>
                <li>Priority customer support</li>
                <li>Detailed analytics and reporting</li>
                <li>Custom branding options</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <% if (next_billing_date) { %>
        <div class="next-billing">
            <h3>ðŸ“… Next Billing Date</h3>
            <p>Your next payment of <strong><%= price_formatted %> <%= currency %></strong> will be charged on <strong><%= next_billing_date %></strong>.</p>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="<%= billing_portal_url %>" class="cta-button">Manage Subscription</a>
        </div>

        <div class="support">
            <h3>ðŸ’¬ Need Help?</h3>
            <p>If you have any questions about your subscription or need assistance, our support team is here to help:</p>
            <p>ðŸ“§ Email: <a href="mailto:<%= support_email %>"><%= support_email %></a></p>
        </div>

        <p>Thank you for choosing <strong><%= app_name %></strong>. We're excited to help you grow your garage business!</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The <%= app_name %> Team</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent to <%= garage_email %> regarding your subscription.</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= app_name %>. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
